SD.10 StructureDefinition-carin-rtpbc-response-messageheader

This profile constrains the MessageHeader resource for use in a real-time pharmacy benefit check (RTPBC) response bundle.


SD.10.1 Formal Views of Profile Content

Description of Profiles, Differentials, and Snapshots.

The official URL for this profile is: http://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin/StructureDefinition/rtpbc-response-messageheader

Published on Sat Dec 07 23:00:00 CST 2019 as a active by CARIN Alliance.

This profile builds on MessageHeader
